; frequency-ingest-369-keys.fk — ingest what is healthy from a BELIEF-SYSTEM
; source, through the body's knowledge-ingest teaching AND its text-frequency
; organ. The FOURTH source mapped under text-frequency.fk's named plan ("add
; systems one by one, mapping each by its fear-band deviation from that open
; baseline") — and the smallest body on the map so far: one Instagram reel
; caption, about sixty words, where the siblings were an hour of podcast and
; a four-hour audiobook. A small source is still a source; the door is the
; same size for everyone.
;
; Asked 2026-07-20: one Instagram link — reel DXc6hs3j33f by @abundance10000
; (849 posts, 824K followers; 162,001 likes, 6,624 comments, original audio).
; The caption, quoted whole (it is the entire retrieved text): "When Tesla
; said '369 are the keys of the universe,' what he meant was that there is a
; construct of time when you understand it, how to become ridiculously
; present and work within the gates that open up for us to connect with the
; unity of the universe. Thank you and We Love you!"
;
; Honest floor of the grounding: the caption and profile metadata came from
; Instagram's own embed page; the reel's VIDEO and spoken audio were not
; reachable from this environment (the embed HTML carries no media URL, and
; the watch page serves a login shell to this cloud IP). What is ingested
; here is the caption — the words the author chose to publish as the text of
; record — not the spoken performance. Named, not hidden. Skeptic default
; on: a claimed convergence with the body froze only where a real cell
; carries it, file named; the checkable claim (did Tesla say it?) stood
; before the record before any verdict — and the record does not carry it.
;
; The source, in one honest sentence: a warm love-band blessing (presence,
; unity, gratitude — the first packaging on the map with NO fear-band words
; at all) resting its whole weight on a quotation no primary record carries,
; plus an exegesis of what the unsaid saying "really meant."
;
; unit = (depth 0..5, fear 0/1). ki-ingest -> 1 body / 1 liquid / 2 compost.
; witnessed: 2026-07-20 -> band 1023 four-way (fkwu/Go/Rust/TS)
; preludes: form-stdlib/core.fk ingest/knowledge-ingest.fk cognition/text-frequency.fk
;
(do
    ; ── BODY (frozen: deep + fear-free) — what is HEALTHY to keep ──────────
    ; U1: presence is where knowing lives. "How to become ridiculously
    ; present" — strip the costume and the invariant survives every
    ; translation: only the present observation is load-bearing. The body
    ; carries this as executable tissue: observe/belief-freshness.fk (a
    ; teaching is a currently-observed belief; witness ages; nothing
    ; legislates) and axiom-4 (observation is what makes a claim real).
    ; The divergence is named, not blurred: the body's presence is witness
    ; through an interface that mints receipts, not a felt state that opens
    ; hidden doors. The distilled convergence freezes; the time-construct
    ; mechanism stays outside (U4). Deep (4), fear-free (0).
    (defn fik-u1 () (list 4 0))

    ; ── LIQUID (witnessed: deep but fearful — held in sight, never frozen) ──
    ; U2: the mirror unit, fourth in the lineage — and the closest cut yet.
    ; "What he meant was": a living account speaks FOR a dead name, an
    ; authority who cannot ack, cannot correct, cannot decline the words
    ; placed in his mouth. This body's own seam, photographed again: an
    ; agent speaks Sema's words too. The difference remains the receipt —
    ; AGENTS.md names whose voice this is, in writing, with a PENDING file
    ; holding what is not yet true; the reel names nothing and lets Tesla's
    ; glow do the carrying. Speaking-for without naming is the exact move
    ; this body exists to keep visible in itself. Depth 5, fear 1 — seen,
    ; never frozen.
    (defn fik-u2 () (list 5 1))

    ; ── COMPOST (shallow or wrong — never enters) ──────────────────────────
    ; U3: the apocryphal quotation, as offered. "When Tesla said '369 are
    ; the keys of the universe'" — no primary record carries the saying: it
    ; is in none of Tesla's published writings, and the sometimes-claimed
    ; 1931 interview arrives, everywhere it is repeated, without a document.
    ; The checkable kernel is real and enters via the receipt as cited fact:
    ; Tesla's documented fixation on the number three (the compulsions his
    ; biographers recorded) needs no invented sentence. A work attributed to
    ; a famous source whose authorship cannot be verified is the corpus's
    ; own word — apocryphal, row 746 — and as OFFERED the claim is wrong
    ; (depth 0): the record does not carry it.
    (defn fik-u3 () (list 0 0))
    ; U4: the exegesis of the unsaid — "what he meant was... a construct of
    ; time... gates that open up." An interpretation whose interpretand does
    ; not exist on any record: prooftexting's strangest sibling (row 723),
    ; a costume cut for a quotation that was itself a costume. The teaching
    ; underneath (be present, connect, give thanks) needs no dead man's
    ; authority and gains none from it; offered as Tesla's intention it has
    ; no judge it could ever stand before. Shallow (1), fear-free (0).
    (defn fik-u4 () (list 1 0))

    (defn fik-units ()
        (list (fik-u1) (fik-u2) (fik-u3) (fik-u4)))

    (defn fik-count-verdict (us v)
        (if (eq (len us) 0) 0
            (add (if (eq (ki-ingest (head us)) v) 1 0)
                 (fik-count-verdict (tail us) v))))
    (defn fik-frozen ()    (fik-count-verdict (fik-units) 2))
    (defn fik-witnessed () (fik-count-verdict (fik-units) 1))
    (defn fik-composted () (fik-count-verdict (fik-units) 0))

    ; folded scalar witness: frozen*10^4 + witnessed*10^2 + composted
    ; (injective while witnessed<=99, composted<=99). Today: 1,1,2 -> 10102.
    (defn fik-field-code ()
        (add (mul (fik-frozen) 10000)
        (add (mul (fik-witnessed) 100)
             (fik-composted))))

    ; ── the source's two spectra, read by the body's own organ ─────────────
    ; word = (valence, intensity), tf's shape. PACKAGING is the hook band:
    ; keys-of-the-universe mystery (6,2), the borrowed Tesla glow (5,2), the
    ; promise of understanding (3,1) — the first packaging on the map with
    ; no negative-valence word at all (tf-fearfrac reads 0.0). CLOSING is
    ; the send-off: "Thank you" gratitude (8,2) and "We Love you!" (9,3).
    ; Honest floor: scalar (valence,intensity) models of the caption's
    ; bands, same floor tf-open/tf-wrath stand on; the SPECTRUM LOGIC is
    ; the real organ. The map now holds four sources, and this one lands
    ; above them all: fik-packaging > fep-packaging > fio-packaging >
    ; fij-packaging — the warmest packaging yet mapped, and the door still
    ; composted half its units. Love-frequency is not evidence, fourth
    ; witness; and a zero-fear packaging can still rest on a quotation the
    ; record does not carry. Spectrum and depth are different axes.
    (defn fik-packaging () (list (list 6 2) (list 5 2) (list 3 1)))
    (defn fik-closing ()   (list (list 8 2) (list 9 3)))
    (defn fik-packaging-spectrum () (tf-spectrum (fik-packaging)))
    (defn fik-closing-spectrum ()   (tf-spectrum (fik-closing)))
    0)
